\"features\"> <h2 class=\"features__title\">Features</h2> <ul class=\"features__item-box\"> <li class=\"features__item\"> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/184eba9f8ce75e781b4f45789d9499ad.jpg\" alt=\"Ebbinghaus\" class=\"features__item-img\"> <h4 class=\"features__itme-text\"> Based on the Ebbinghaus method </h4> </li> <li class=\"features__item\"> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/77904d03a4ce6045e5f51ceae1b50ee4.jpg\" alt=\"One Place\" class=\"features__item-img\"> <h4 class=\"features__itme-text\"> All in one place </h4> </li> <li class=\"features__item\"> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/0c4deb8e2dfaac546a1ab4d7f1ebecc0.jpg\" alt=\"Maskot\" class=\"features__item-img\"> <h4 class=\"features__itme-text\"> Made by a learner, for learners </h4> </li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"how-it-works\"> <h2 class=\"how-it-works__title\">How it works</h2> <div class=\"how-it-works__content\"> <div class=\"how-it-works__number-group\"> <h3 class=\"how-it-works__number\">1</h3> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/e6272b19fbfed7c40289d34b5cac3397.svg\" alt=\"line\" class=\"how-it-works__line\"> <h3 class=\"how-it-works__number\">2</h3> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/e6272b19fbfed7c40289d34b5cac3397.svg\" alt=\"line\" class=\"how-it-works__line\"> <h3 class=\"how-it-works__number\">3</h3> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/e6272b19fbfed7c40289d34b5cac3397.svg\" alt=\"line\" class=\"how-it-works__line\"> <h3 class=\"how-it-works__number\">4</h3> </div> </div> <div class=\"how-it-works__blocks-group\"> <div class=\"how-it-works__block\"> <h4 class=\"how-it-works__block-title\">Add</h4> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/8cc8a2a098f5342e66b06234552c490f.svg\" alt=\"Add\" class=\"how-it-works__block-img\"> </div> <div class=\"how-it-works__block\"> <h4 class=\"how-it-works__block-title\">Learn</h4> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/cf8e17b8b0d00c0c32f3f128b8e7ccab.svg\" alt=\"Learn\" class=\"how-it-works__block-img\"> </div> <div class=\"how-it-works__block\"> <h4 class=\"how-it-works__block-title\">Repeat</h4> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/bb84eecab99273d5628b2407c17cdcef.svg\" alt=\"Repeat\" class=\"how-it-works__block-img\"> </div> <div class=\"how-it-works__block\"> <h4 class=\"how-it-works__block-title\">Remember</h4> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/699416ba8efef7fadb0b2ae6e4915718.svg\" alt=\"Remember\" class=\"how-it-works__block-img\"> </div> </div> </div> <div class=\"vwa\"> <h2 class=\"vwa__title\">VWA</h2> <div class=\"vwa__content\"> <div class=\"vwa__author-group\"> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/ffd2a32e5d0d24eebcdfcb3da594e323.jpg\" alt=\"Author with mascot\" class=\"vwa__author-img\"> <div class=\"vwa__author-info\"> <h4 class=\"vwa__author-title\">Yehor Kantsyr</h4> <p class=\"vwa__author-subtitle\">(Creator of LingoIQ)</p> </div> </div> <p class=\"vwa__pharagrph\"> Hi! I’m Yehor, and LingoIQ is my VWA project. <br> I created this site to make language learning <b>simpler and more structured.</b> Here, you can find words, grammar rules, and learning tools <b>all in one place.</b> <br> The site includes a program I developed using <b>Hermann Ebbinghaus’ spaced repetition method</b> to help you remember words efficiently. It’s designed for students, migrants, and anyone eager to learn languages, offering <b>clear structures and easy navigation.</b> <br> With LingoIQ, I want to give everyone the same opportunity I had: a clear path to mastering a new language. </p> </div> </div> </div> </main> <footer class=\"container footer\"> <a href=\"#\" class=\"footer-panel__logo-link\"> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/c5c8c21b7ca2c1915e80ab79b7cc8964.svg\" alt=\"logo\" class=\"footer-panel__logo-img\"> </a> <div class=\"footer__social-media\"> <a href=\"#\" class=\"footer__social-media-link\"> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/7c8d573dbb3f42509cb7143fd47b8ee1.svg\" alt=\"Youtube\" class=\"footer__social-media-icon\"> </a> <a href=\"#\" class=\"footer__social-media-link\"> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/e3587468a5587b238fb7eec11807d453.svg\" alt=\"GitHub\" class=\"footer__social-media-icon\"> </a> <a href=\"#\" class=\"footer__social-media-link\"> <img src=\"/LingoIQ/022796b137a5a1cb441588c2c5089585.svg\" alt=\"Instagram